# droplist — accounts to always recommend unfollowing.
#
# One username per line (without the leading @). Lines starting with '#' and
# blank lines are ignored. Matching is case-insensitive.
#
# This is the exact inverse of keeplist.txt: a handle listed here is
# forced into the Unfollow bucket regardless of score or inferred keep-
# signals (close friend, favorited, DM activity, brand class). It does NOT
# auto-unfollow — it only changes the audit recommendation; you still act
# manually inside Instagram.
#
# A restricted account stays in Review even if droplisted (the restricted
# floor wins — restricted means "look at this before any drop call").
#
# A handle present in BOTH this file and keeplist.txt is a
# contradiction and is a HARD error at load — fix it before the run scores.
#
# Examples (commented out):
# an_account_i_keep_meaning_to_drop
# brand_i_stopped_caring_about
